\section{Problem 1}
	\subsection{}
	the power function is $$\beta(\theta)=P_\theta(x\in R)$$
	The significance of the test is $$\alpha=\sup_{\theta\in\Theta_0}P_\theta(x\in R)=\frac{1}{2^9}$$
	\subsection{}
	the value of parameter is $\theta=0.1$ ,thus ,the power of the test is $$\beta(\theta)=P_\theta(x\in R)=\frac{1+9^{10}}{10^{10}}$$
